GGZ Community - a web-based GGZ community platform
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Copy the 'web' directory into the document root of your web server,
and point your browser to the pages.

Read setup/setup.txt in order to install the SQL schmema files
and so on.

All the icons are from kggz, they need improvement.

What has improved compared to the old rankings pages?
-----------------------------------------------------
* flexible shared OOP-style PHP engine
* internationalization
* clean HTML and CSS design
* security: HTTPS and login procedures
* logical partitioning of the modules

